Subject: Verify that client 3.0.3.1 supports macOS 15 Sequoia
Description:
I looked through all the documentation for Server version 5.9.4.0 and Client 3.0.3.1, but couldn't find any specific information that says "YES, macOS 15 is officially supported". 

When EPP was CoSoSys, I could pretty much guarantee that day 1 release of macOS would already work, but things have changed and I don't know how fast things work at Netwrix.
Solution_Comment__c: Informed of compatibility of 5940 with macOS 15.
